          <para styleclass="Body Table">To do <text styleclass="VariableName">Force Analysis</text> of the <text styleclass="VariableName">Conjugate Cams</text>, you must select the <text styleclass="Element">Conjugate-Cam FB </text>in the <text styleclass="Element">Configure Power Source dialog-box</text>.</para>
