    <para styleclass="Heading3_atocs_"><anchor id="CPS-CONJUGATECAM"><keywords><keyword>Configure Power Source<keyword>Conjugate Cam</keyword></keyword></keywords></anchor><text styleclass="Heading4 Toggle_atocs_">How to open the Configure the Power Source </text></para>
