      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td>
          <para styleclass="Normal"><image src="MD-DIALOG-CONFIGUREPOWERSOURCE-CONJUGATECAMFB-0.ipp" scale="-99.90%" styleclass="Image Caption" figurelistinclude="0"><caption><![CDATA[DEFAULT: Configure Power Source dialog-box]]></caption></image></para>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td style="height:115px;">
          <para styleclass="HowTo STEP"><text styleclass="VariableName">Configure the Power Source</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><table styleclass="PopupTable2" rowcount="1" colcount="1">
            <tr style="vertical-align:top">
              <td style="border-top:none; border-right:none; border-bottom:none;">
                <list id="10" type="ol" listtype="decimal" formatstring="&#37;&#48;&#58;&#115;&#46;" format-charset="DEFAULT_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="Body Table" style="font-family:&apos;Segoe UI Semibold&apos;; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold; color:#000000;">
                  <li styleclass="Body Table">Click the <text styleclass="VariableName">Kinematics-Tree</text> tab in the <text styleclass="Interface">Element Explorer</text><text styleclass="VariableName">&#32;</text></li>
                  <li styleclass="Body Table"><text styleclass="Body Text">Click the </text><text styleclass="VariableName">Kinematics-Chain</text><text styleclass="Body Text"> that includes the </text><text styleclass="VariableName">Follower Part </text></li>
                  <li styleclass="Body Table"><text styleclass="Body Text">Right-click the </text><text styleclass="VariableName">Kinematic-Chain</text></li>
                  <li styleclass="Body Table"><text styleclass="Body Text">Click </text><text styleclass="Interface2">Configure Power-Source</text><text styleclass="Body Text"> to open the </text><text styleclass="Element">Configure Power-Source dialog-box</text><text styleclass="SeeAlso"> - see image above</text></li>
                </list>
                <para styleclass="Body Text">The <text styleclass="Element">Pin-Joint </text><image src="Red-14-1b.gif" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Image Caption" figurelistinclude="0"></image> is the <text styleclass="Interface2">default</text>&#32;<text styleclass="Parameter-Header">Motor Element</text> (<text styleclass="VariableName">Power-Source)</text>&#32;<text styleclass="SeeAlso">- see image above</text></para>
                <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#993300;" /></para>
                <para styleclass="Body Text">Notice also the <text styleclass="VariableName">Motor Symbol</text><image src="Red-14-2.gif" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Image Caption" figurelistinclude="0"></image> to the left of the <text styleclass="Element">Pin-Joint </text><text styleclass="SeeAlso">- see image above</text></para>
                <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#993300;" /></para>
                <para styleclass="Body Table"><text styleclass="Body Text">In the </text><text styleclass="Element">Configure Power-Source dialog-box</text><text styleclass="Body Text"> - </text><text styleclass="SeeAlso">see image below</text></para>
                <list id="10" type="ol" listtype="decimal" formatstring="&#37;&#48;&#58;&#115;&#46;" format-charset="DEFAULT_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="Body Table" style="font-family:&apos;Segoe UI Semibold&apos;; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold; color:#000000;">
                  <li styleclass="Body Table"><text styleclass="Body Text">Click the </text><text styleclass="Element">Conjugate Cam</text><image src="Red-14-3.gif" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Image Caption" figurelistinclude="0"></image><text styleclass="Body Text"> in the list of elements - </text><text styleclass="SeeAlso">see image below</text></li>
                </list>
                <para styleclass="Body Text">The <text styleclass="Element">Conjugate-Cam</text><image src="Red-14-3.gif" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Image Caption" figurelistinclude="0"></image> replaces the <text styleclass="Element">Pin-Joint</text> as the <text styleclass="Parameter-Header">Motor Element</text><image src="Red-14-3.gif" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Image Caption" figurelistinclude="0"></image><text styleclass="VariableName"> (Power-Source) - </text><text styleclass="SeeAlso">see image below</text></para>
                <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#993300;" /></para>
                <para styleclass="Body Text">Notice the <text styleclass="VariableName">Motor Symbol</text><image src="Red-14-4.gif" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Image Caption" figurelistinclude="0"></image> is now to the left of the <text styleclass="Element">Conjugate-Cam &#160;</text><text styleclass="SeeAlso">- see image below</text></para>
                <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#993300;" /></para>
                <list id="11" type="ol" listtype="decimal" formatstring="&#37;&#48;&#58;&#115;&#46;" format-charset="DEFAULT_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="6" styleclass="Body Table" style="font-family:&apos;Segoe UI Semibold&apos;; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold; color:#000000;">
                  <li styleclass="Body Table">&#32;<text styleclass="HowTo STEP">Click </text><image src="OK-tiny-11-15.png" scale="100.00%" styleclass="HowTo STEP" figurelistinclude="0"></image><text styleclass="HowTo STEP">&#32;</text><text styleclass="Body Text">to close the dialog-box</text><text styleclass="HowTo STEP">.</text><text styleclass="VariableName">&#32;</text></li>
                </list>
              </td>
            </tr>
          </table></para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text">Now you can do <text styleclass="VariableName">Contact-Force Analysis</text> for the <text styleclass="VariableName">Conjugates-Cams</text>.</para>
